        <Parent_String>orders to pay [300193968], negotiable instruments [300191321], exchange media (objects) [300387350], Exchange Media (hierarchy name) [300037221], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
